</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Worker_Adjustment_and_Retraining_Notification_Act&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Worker Adjustment and Retraining Notification Act (page does not exist)">Worker Adjustment and Retraining Notification Act</a> (WARN Act)
</li>
